        p.
          The <a href="http://imdb.org">Internet Movie Database</a> is a brilliant online resource for movie fans.
          Signigicantly, it owes its vast cache of information to volunteers who add information.
          The data is vetted, and perhaps surprisingly, is the most accurate and widespread source of information about movies.
